casebody.data:
Jacob SZAFRANSKI, petitioner,
v.
Karla DUNSTON. No. 15-912. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 29, 2016.

Motion of American Association of Pro-Life Obstetricians and Gynecologists for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Appellate Court of Illinois, First District denied.
